Fig. 3 is an enlarged view of a detail of Fig. 2.
Fig. 4 is an exploded perspective view of an ending pin of the drum shaft and a washer belonging to the driving unit of the washing machine according to the present invention;
Fig. 5 is basically the same as Fig. 3, except for the fact that it refers to an additional embodiment of the driving unit of the washing machine according to the present invention;
Fig. 6 is an axial sectional view of the washer of Fig. 4;
Fig. 7 is an axial sectional of a pulley inserted into the threaded distal section of the ending pin of the drum shaft.
